{"tid":526956,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Pokemon Go 玩家要注意！部分 iPhone、iPad 無得再玩","createTime":"2018-01-12T07:09:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-12T08:45:28.000Z","uid":147376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4972847d55cae19840debe17c522919c6aa1d2db","tid":526956,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T07:09:55.000Z","msg":"Pokemon Go 熱潮雖然已過，但仍然有唔少人仲有繼續玩落去，不過若果你係 Apple 用家就要留意：<span style=\"color: red;\">Pokemon Go 下月底開始只會支援 iOS 11 用家繼續使用。</span>換句話說，如果你唔及時更新 iPhone 或 iPad，又或者用緊未能支援 iOS 11 裝置的話，你好快就無得四圍捉小精靈喇。&nbsp;開發商之所以作出呢個決定，係因為佢地支援為遊戲加入新元素，好讓玩家有更佳體驗，而舊版 iOS 已經唔再應付到相關新增元素，因此作出呢個決定。據報，<span style=\"color: red;\">由 3月份開始，未能得到 iOS 11 更新的一系列 Apple 產品，包括 iPhone 5、iPhone 5c、iPad 2、iPad mini 等都唔再玩得到 Pokemon Go。</span>若然想繼續玩，只需要於支援 iOS 11 的裝置上登入就可以繼續捉小精靈了。"},{"pid":"f2a18afa586f5a469beb3d683c3ce6a40b2e779e","tid":526956,"uid":7240,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T07:11:14.000Z","msg":"Who cares? 垃圾驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d6613d5bf8b18122c5b6831f0cc0f4f627cf627","tid":526956,"uid":10338,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T07:15:20.000Z","msg":"都無人玩架啦"},{"pid":"27edbfcbb0f57fe7c8c74bab2330e16e13d5d7c5","tid":526956,"uid":26200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T07:33:58.000Z","msg":"用arkit?"},{"pid":"14c1a0b58fe72296b43fa797864adda8e789ba32","tid":526956,"uid":57835,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T08:34:56.000Z","msg":"咁舊既機都係新聞？"},{"pid":"fe2abba96c195d5f45715354ae0ab9418131580a","tid":526956,"uid":61094,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"14c1a0b58fe72296b43fa797864adda8e789ba32","tid":526956,"uid":57835,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T08:34:56.000Z","msg":"咁舊既機都係新聞？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T08:42:45.000Z","msg"